name: The first jumpscare video I saw
description: I remember the first time I was on the Internet, I would always open a video on my facebook link or watch random on youtube, as well as from my brother's cell phone. And yet there is a video monumental enough for me. It was a video that initially showed a swaying  in a living room. Then suddenly a ghostly jumpscare appeared, which suddenly scared me. And I was beyond that, that face was reached by one of the exorcist characters.
